high_descs: Turn around, go to the table with the microwave on it across the room.
Take a potato out of the microwave.
Turn around, walk towards the oven, then turn right and go to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink. Turn the water on then off. Take the potato from the sink.
Go to the black stand to the left of the sink.
Put the potato on the lower right corner of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed potato on a stand.

high_descs: Open microwave, take out potato on right
place potato in sink, fill sink with water, pick up potato
Go to black table with green melon
Place potato on black table to right of green melon
anns.task_desc: Wash potato, place next to melon

high_descs: take an egg out of the microwave
walk over to the kitchen sink
place the egg inside the kitchen sink and rinse it, then pick it back up
walk over to the black shelves to the left of the kitchen counter
place the egg on top of the black shelves
anns.task_desc: place a rinsed egg on top of the black shelves in the kitchen
